item.title: Cause of infection of COVID-19 in Toronto
item.description: Abstract Nowadays, people are generally concerned about COVID-19. In this paper, I used “COVID-19 Cases in Toronto” data set from OPENDATA Toronto to study the characteristics of confirmed and probable infected people and came to the conclusion that who is more likely to get infection of COVID-19. Thus, we can use scientific methods to reduce the chance of getting infection of COVID-19. Introduction At the moment, COVID-19 has a great impact on people all over the world.
